    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/pc/ontologies/2026/4/untitled-ontology-2#kripesemantic">
        <rdfs:comment>A Kripke model consists of:possible worlds, accessibility relation between worlds, a valuation assigning to each propositional variable the set of worlds where it is true</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Class>
    


